  <description>
    <p>
      Tac Writer is a GTK4 and libadwaita desktop application for planning,
      structuring, and writing academic texts with the Tecnica da Argumentacao
      Continua (TAC) workflow.
    </p>
    <p>
      It helps students and researchers organize paragraphs, track writing
      progress, manage projects, and export drafts in common academic formats.
    </p>
